  <original-body>Passing the :limit option to a named scope has no affect on the query generated.

e.g.

@@@ Ruby

class Product
  named_scope :most_ordered, :order =&gt; 'ordered_count DESC'
end

# We want the three most ordered products
Product.most_ordered(3)
@@@

Generates the following sql:

SELECT * FROM `products` ORDER BY ordered_count DESC</original-body>
